title: Masanaga
text:
Masanaga (written: 政長, 正長, 昌寿 or 雅永) is a masculine Japanese given name. Notable people with the name include:

Hatakeyama Masanaga (畠山 政長, 1442–1493), Japanese daimyō
Masanaga Kageyama (影山 雅永, born 1967), Japanese footballer and manager
Kōriki Masanaga (高力 正長, 1558–1599), Japanese daimyō
Miyoshi Masanaga (三好 政長, 1508–1549), Japanese samurai and daimyō
Yonekura Masanaga (米倉 昌寿, 1793–1863), Japanese daimyō
